<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Processes other than fire, including erosion and rock fall, likely disturb stands. Although <i>Selaginella bigelovii </i>can sprout following fire, stands probably do not burn severely in its rocky surroundings. Crevices protect the rhizomes.</div>
